          <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/forum">Forums</a> › <a href="/forum/stanza">Stanza Support</a></div>                              <h2>How do I create text for reading on Stanza?</h2>                                                  <div class="clear-block">
            <div id="node-1712" class="node">



      <span class="submitted">Mon, 11/30/2009 - 16:11 — Skinny Cricket</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <p>I would like to write content that can be read on Stanza.  What file format should I write to?  Are there any special considerations with regard to column width etc. to allow my text to fit properly on an iPhone/iPod screen?  What is the best font to use?  Any suggestions or directions to a source for this information would be appreciated.</p>
<p>Thank you...</p>
<p>Skinny Cricket</p>
