<div id="comments"><a id="comment-6229"></a>
<div class="comment comment-published odd">

  <div class="clear-block">
      <span class="submitted">Mon, 11/30/2009 - 19:29 — kjk</span>
  
  
  <div class="picture">
  </div>

    <h3><a href="/node/1712#comment-6229" class="active">You can create in a variety</a></h3>

    <div class="content">
      <p>You can create in a variety of formats-from simple .txt to Word .doc to web .html-Stanza Desktop will convert it to readable format for the Touch and iPhone.</p>
<p>The native format for Stanza iPhone is ePub. The free program Sigil is capable of editing ePubs. There is also a Windows program called Atlantis that can apparently save in ePub format-but I've never tried it. Good luck!</p>
          </div>
  </div>

