    <h3><a href="/node/1712#comment-6304" class="active">Thanks for the info.  This is</a></h3>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Thanks for the info.  This is really helpful, and I checked out Atlantis which really looks good.</p>
<p>One more question...using Stanza on an i-device, is it possible to highlight text in the e-book or e-article so the user can copy the text to another application?  My concept involves a lesson-plan approach where it might be desirable for the user to copy content in this manner.</p>
<p>...Skinny Cricket</p>
