    <h3><a href="/node/1712#comment-6305" class="active">I just tried it-I cannot use</a></h3>

    <div class="content">
      <p>I just tried it-I cannot use Apple's built in Copy/Paste to work in Stanza iPhone. Clicking on a section of text opens Stanza's Annotation editor-clicking on the text in that brings up the familiar iPhone copy/paste cursors/magnifying glass..but i don't see a copy command. Looks like its not implemented correctly.</p>
          </div>
  </div>

